title: Microsoft Office Select Edition 2016 v16.0.4300.1000
description:
Microsoft Office Select Edition 2016 v16.0.4300.1000
Office Related | OS: Windows Server/7/8/8.1/10 (x64x86) | 5.4 GB + 6.7 GB
Original Install File | Update: November 2015 | Language: English

Here is a new version of Microsoft Office 2016 - update of one of the most important products of the company. Microsoft Office 2016 well demonstrates how today has changed the approach to create documents and work with them.

any of us are beginning to work on the same computer, it continues on the other, as demonstrated in the third, simultaneously managing to make minor changes for laptop, tablet or smartphone. Therefore, Office 2016 tried to make conceptually different. Almost all of the key elements in it have been developed from scratch, and applications oriented to a single style of work, regardless of the hardware platform. They are designed to provide the usual functional on any device, automatically adjusting its interface to the parameters of the current screen and the available system resources. Download version to cwer.ws, you will receive a work set with the possibility of full activation.

The previous version, Office 2013 was released two years ago, at the beginning of 2013 - by today's standards for a long time. At Microsoft, apparently, talked the same way: in January 2015 the company announced that the new release, Office 2016 will be released in the second half of this year, and in March introduced a beta version for developers. And finally, today, September 22, 2015, an official release and the start of sales of the new office suite from Microsoft - Microsoft Office 2016. As provided in the cwer.ws version of the product is decorated in an iso image with the possibility of Russian or English interface and convenient activator.

Requisiti:
- Computer e processore: 1 gigahertz (GHz) o superiore, 64-bit x86-o. CPU con istruzioni SSE2
- Memoria (RAM): 1 gigabyte (GB) di RAM (32-bit). 2 gigabyte (GB) di RAM (64-bit)
- Disco rigido: 3,0 gigabyte (GB) di spazio libero
- Display: accelerazione hardware grafica richiede una scheda grafica con supporto per DirectX10 e una risoluzione di 1024 x 576
- Sistema operativo: Windows 7, Windows 8, 10, Windows Server 2008 R2 o 2012 prodotti applicazioni di Office di Windows Server
